[Analysis on adult health life expectancy in Shanghai].

[Article in Chinese; Abstract available in Chinese from the publisher]

Fang B(1), Wang CF(2), Yu HT(2), Chen L(2), Cai RZ(2), Qian NS(2), Xia T(2), Wu 
